REQUIREMENTS
🔹 Functional Requirements
System must display quiz questions
System must accept user input
System must evaluate answers
System must calculate score
System must display result
🔹 Non-Functional Requirements
Simple and user-friendly interface
Fast execution (console-based)
Low memory usage
Portable (runs on any C compiler)
🔹 Hardware Requirements
Basic computer system
Keyboard (for input)
🔹 Software Requirements
C Compiler (e.g., GCC, Turbo C)
Operating System (Windows/Linux/Mac)
